data.name: toolStripTextBoxFilter.ToolTipText
data.value: Enter text here to filter displayed frames. You can enter: 1. A hex string (e.g. 22 F1 00), to show only frames where the frame data contains that hex string. 2. A hex string (e.g. 18DAF100), to show only frames where the CAN ID or Ethernet source/target address contains the hex string. 3. A string (e.g. DM1), to show only frames where the content in the service column or symbolic column contains the string. 4. A time period (e.g. 400ms), to show only frames where the delta from the previous message exceeds the time period.

data.name: toolStripComboBoxEcuFilter.ToolTipText
data.value: Select a device here to filter displayed frames to only those sent to or received from that device.
